RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT b.Customer_No FROM Oltms_Customer b WHERE b.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND b.Record_Stat = 'O' ORDER BY Customer_Name1

SELECT a.TRADE_REF_NO FROM TLTB_UPLOAD_MASTER a WHERE a.PROCESS_STATUS='P' AND a.BRANCH=GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH and a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(b.Version_No) FROM Tltbs_Upload_Master b WHERE a.TRADE_REF_NO = b.TRADE_REF_NO AND a.source_code = b.source_code AND a.branch = b.branch)
